chunk_content: Deploy a fine-tuned modelOnce your model is fine-tuned, you can deploy the model and can use it in your own application. You can't deploy a fine-tuned model from the deployments page or the playground page in Azure AI Studio. The only way, currently, to deploy a fine-tuned model is from the model details page for that model.When you deploy the model, you make the model available for inferencing, and that incurs an hourly hosting charge. Fine-tuned models, however, can be stored in Azure AI Studio at no cost until you're ready to use them.[!INCLUDE Fine-tuning deletion]> [!NOTE]> Only one deployment is permitted for a fine-tuned model. An error message is displayed if you select an already-deployed fine-tuned model.You can monitor the progress of your deployment on the Deployments page in Azure AI Studio.
